title: USC Norris gala honors Dana and David Dornsife (USC - University of Southern California)
text: ( Source : USC - University of Southern California ) Dana and David Dornsife were honored for their contributions to the university and its health enterprises Oct. 10 at the annual USC Norris Comprehensive Cancer Center gala. Actor Pierce
